@node "Copyright"

                 @{apen 2}@{b}COPYRIGHT AND FREEWARE@{ub}@{apen 1}

@{b}PtpDigCam Copyright © 2006 Christophe GENRE@{ub} All rights reserved.

PtpDigCam is freeware and may be freely spread, if no file is added, deleted
or modified.

@endnode

@node "Introduction"

PtpDigCam software purpose is to allow PTP digital camera owner to :
   - scan for camera PTP objects (images, videos, sounds) contents
   - download selected objects from the camera,
   - delete selected objects in the camera,
   - get and set the camera current time.

This software runs on :
   - A Pegasos running MorphOS

NOTE: The digital camera must be compliant with the "Picture Tranfer Protocol"
      (PTP) standard commands.

