@node "Future"

PtpDigCam software enhancements could be the followings :

   - Correct user problems
   - Add thumbnail display and selection panel
   - Add a toolbar with image and text buttons 
   - Display images EXIF data

A part of PtpDigCam may be used to make a VHI driver (if support come back)
A part of PtpDigCam may be used to make a Poseidon class

@endnode
